公司 (<span style=\"color: red;\">招商銀行</span>、招商局國際 、招商局置地)<br />\n3. 華潤（集團）有限公司 (華潤創業、華潤電力、華潤置地、華潤水泥控股、華潤燃氣)<br />\n4. 中國光大集團股份公司<br />\n<br />\n其餘在港國企<br />\n5. 中國電信集團公司<br />\n6. <span style=\"color: red;\">中國聯合網絡通信</span>集團有限公司<br />\n7. <span style=\"color: red;\">中國移動</span>通信集團公司<br />\n8. 華為技術有限公司<br />\n9. 中國<span style=\"color: red;\">工商銀行</span>股份有限公司<br />\n10. 中國<span style=\"color: red;\">建設銀行</span>股份有限公司<br />\n11. 中國建築股份有限公司<br />\n12. 中國農業銀行股份有限公司<br />\n13. 中國<span style=\"color: red;\">平安保險</span>（集團）股份有限公司<br />\n14. <span style=\"color: red;\">中國人壽</span>保險（集團）公司<br />\n</span></strong>"},{"pid":"1f4cd6d6541a2f5d2d99d187450eaf6b9c7cd7ad","tid":1715802,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:40:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07538f25dd2f22b7e01d4fb24e23e5b572a6f9dc","tid":1715802,"uid":152225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:40:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80a27646159b3887e8beb80effc9b4340fb1295f","tid":1715802,"uid":28575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:41:51.000Z","msg":"放工時間黎個大集合, 二百萬人FULL GEAR行吐公入去"},{"pid":"77eebf656b3dc7dc0dc23f352674eaa2908a5156","tid":1715802,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:42:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e14664b35addd1d8bcabe9d0f5b498468eafbfca","tid":1715802,"uid":59447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:42:45.000Z","msg":"中大仔值得支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69d1c1de39e79be2df7e359ab0b22273cda326e9","tid":1715802,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim